title: Continuos Pieces - 9/11
description:
CONTINUOS PIECES - 9/11
2.5GB XVID AVI
2hrs24min38sec

A 9/11 investigative documentary. 

Including witnesses,photographers and videographers as well as various 
experts and guests to show what did and did not happen on that day! 

The video also exposes some disinformation and offers a conclusion
that could clear up many of the questions concerning September 11 2001.
